org.gvsig.fmap.dal.feature.spi

Interface FeatureStoreProvider

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataFactoryUnit, DataStoreProvider, Disposable, DynObject, DynObject_v2
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    FeatureCacheProvider, FeatureStoreProvider_v2, JDBCStoreProvider
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractFeatureStoreProvider, AbstractMemoryStoreProvider, CSVStoreProvider, DBFStoreProvider, DGNStoreProvider, DWGStoreProvider, DXFStoreProvider, FeatureTypeToStoreProviderAdapter, GMLDataStoreProvider, GMLStoreProvider, GPEStoreProvider, JDBCStoreProviderBase, JExcelStoreProvider, JsonStoreProvider, KMLStoreProvider, MemoryStoreProvider, OGRDataStoreProvider, OGRStoreProvider, SeismicStoreProvider, SHPStoreProvider, SimpleReaderStoreProvider, SimpleSequentialReaderStoreProvider, WFSStoreProvider

    public interface FeatureStoreProvider
extends DataStoreProvider
    Interface for all feature based data providers.

    A FeatureStoreProvier must have a contructor like this:

    FeatureStoreProvider(DataStoreParameters, FeatureStoreProviderServices)
